snippet.title: EVE Online: Lifeblood (Oct 2017) Expansion Teaser
snippet.description:
On 24 October, the EVE Online: Lifeblood expansion will be released. There will be major updates to moon mining, Refineries will be introduced and much more. Read more: http://updates.eveonline.com/date/2017-10-24/

Start playing EVE for free at http://www.eveonline.com
